;
IFSAY giant_lizard?
      ECHO ALL Menelian says, "The slow-moving giant lizard is a peaceful vegetarian, but when angered it has a nasty bite."
ENDIF
IFSAY giant_lizards?
      ECHO ALL Menelian says, "The slow-moving giant lizard is a peaceful vegetarian, but when angered it has a nasty bite."
ENDIF
;
IFSAY boar?
      ECHO PLAYER Menelian says, "Wild boars are very hostile, but they are hunted for their tasty flesh. Their larger cousin, the giant boar, is extremely vicious, and their larger brain leads me to believe that they in fact posess a cunning, evil intellect. The flesh of the larger variety is much less useful than the wild boars, as is the way with most higher predators."
ENDIF
