      ECHO ALL Menelian says, "A single rat, or even a giant rat, is a minor threat to a person. Yet this urban threat does not persist for no reason. Consider some intriguing facts:  even a fat rat can squeeze through a hole the size of a coin, can chew its way through a brick wall in under an hour, is resistant to most diseases, and can swim for hours if need be."
ENDIF
;
IFSAY gnomen?
	ECHO ALL Menelian says, "The gnomen are a race of inhuman, thoroughly evil creatures that live in shadow and feed upon fear. They live in Mirdaal, and some of them wield necromantic spells. I believe their origin must be extraplanar."
ENDIF
;
IFSAY harpy?
	ECHO ALL Menelian says, "The harpies are brutal woman-birds that hate all life. Their hair is known to contain a brilliant azure pigment, and their leader is Iriezza."
ENDIF
