	ECHO ALL Menelian says, "A powerful harpy, and their leader."
ENDIF
;
IFSAY arachnid?
	ECHO ALL Menelian says, "Like many creatures that thrive in Mirdaal, the shadow arachnid originates from a plane beyond Andor, probably the same place as the gnomen. Their webs are formed out of a horrendous, nightmarish material that aside from immobilizing and slow a victim, can even feed upon their life-force."
ENDIF
