ITEM 0 390 ADJ1=164
EXTEND 0 held together with a network of wires
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
The skeleton is held together with a network of wires. Someone has gone through a painstaking time of bleaching it and piecing it all together.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 1 1577 ADJ1=87
;
IFPREVERB GO 1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO OTHERS %N joins Menelian over at the dark corner.
	MOVE 1803
ENDIF
;
ITEM 2 432
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
The paintings show various pictures of every race and creature imagineable, including quite a few you have never seen (nor want to). Various cutaways are shown of each, displaying skeletal structure, muscle tissue, organs, etc.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 4 1576 ADJ1=143
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 4
The glass case contains an assortment of insects, preserved and mounted on pins.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 4
The glass case contains an assortment of insects, preserved and mounted on pins.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 5 201
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM ON 5
On the desk are a pile of illegible notes and a fossilized skull carved out at the top to serve as a candleholder.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 6 352 ADJ1=1114
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 6
You have no idea what type of animal the fossilized skull came from, but it appears to be some sort of reptile. It has rows of broken teeth, but its horns are still intact. It has been carved out at the top to contain an uneven black candle.
*DESCRIPTION_END
PUT 6 640 ADJ1=25
ITEM 7 277 ADJ1=396
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 7
The book shelf is bending under the weight of its contents:  endless books
in languages you have never seen, tightly packed scrolls, and even a few
stone tablets with runes chiseled into their surface. A few intriguing
jars serve as bookends.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 8 356
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 8
The jars contain a variety of substances. One is full of various eyes
preserved in some foul-smelling liquid. Another contains a fetal pig.
Yet another contains the brain of some animal.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFVERB SMELL 8
	ECHO PLAYER The jars smell awful.
ENDIF
